examples.en: We caught a glimpse of someone lurking around the corner.
She didn't see the figure lurking behind the bushes.
There are two men lurking about my gate, making me nervous.
I could sense the hostility lurking behind her polite facade.
Death could be seen lurking in the corner of the painting.
She could tell there was someone out there lurking in the shadows.
They wondered what might be lurking in the lightless corners of the basement.
